        {
            "title": "內地A股午市先升後跌 滬指收跌15點 深指失守萬三關收挫0.76%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外圍市況造好，未能帶挈內地A股，滬深兩市股指午市齊齊先升後倒跌，近期強勢的鋰業股亦受壓，兩隻A+H的鋰業股均先揚後挫報跌收場。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指經過早市幾乎全程報升後，午後初段曾再往上衝，但未能升越早市高位3967點，未幾更掉頭下走，於下午約1時35分左右開始轉跌，最低見3927點，跌19點，與早市最多升21點時完全兩樣；滬指最後收報3931點，跌15點或0.4%，成交7113.41億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日呈高開低走，初段曾見13226點，升145點，其後便開始拾級下滑，於早市中段開始轉跌，午後曾經倒升，但維持不足半小時又再轉跌，一度失守萬三點，最低報12970點，跌109點，尾市於萬三點爭持；深指最後收報12980點，跌99點或0.76%，成交9968.47億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌23點或0.51%，以4564點收市；創業板指數跌34點或1.12%，報3042點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鋰業股早市原本持續強勢，午後卻逐步下滑。天齊鋰業(09696)A股(002466.SZ)收挫2.01%，報62.31元；贛鋒鋰業(01772)A股(002460.SZ)亦跌1.86%，報71.27元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"天齊鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/09696-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"天齊鋰業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/09696-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">天齊鋰業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，寧德時代(03750)H股基石投資者禁售期屆滿，今日開始可以售股，H股今日明顯捱沽，寧德時代A股(300750.SZ)亦受壓，收跌2.99%，報379.39元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅銀行股午後重力減弱，中國銀行(03988)A股(601988.SH)升幅收窄至4%，報6.24元；建設銀行(00939)A股(601939.SH)升幅也縮至3.15%，報9.82元。農業銀行(01288)A股(601288.SH)更倒跌0.73%，報8.16元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15442056-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%b8%82%e5%85%88%e5%8d%87%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c15%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89%e9%97%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 15:10:27",
